{{Top|leg}}
The '''boyy'lo''' was a plant from the planet [[Nimban/Legends|Nimban]]. Its succulent berries were well-protected, requiring the primitive [[Nimbanel/Legends|Nimbanels]] to develop sophisticated tools to harvest them.

